  m_Name: Dialogue guard kill
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: Assembly-CSharp::SODialogue
  Characters: []
  Nodes:
  - IndexCharacterRight: 0
    IndexCharacterLeft: 0
    IndexCharacterFocus: 0
    IndexExpression: 0
    IndexEmotion: 0
    Text: The goblin grins at the sight. She wants to see what this bandit leader
      is made out of.
  - IndexCharacterRight: 0
    IndexCharacterLeft: 0
    IndexCharacterFocus: 0
    IndexExpression: 0
    IndexEmotion: 0
    Text: This will be a good excuse to kill him afterwards.
  - IndexCharacterRight: 0
    IndexCharacterLeft: 0
    IndexCharacterFocus: 0
    IndexExpression: 0
    IndexEmotion: 0
    Text: The gunwitch tells you that you have to stop him. She cannot let a young
      guard die for nothing.
  - IndexCharacterRight: 0
    IndexCharacterLeft: 0
    IndexCharacterFocus: 0
    IndexExpression: 0
    IndexEmotion: 0
    Text: The goblin is sad she doesn't get to see some tortuing but I guess the
      guard beign alive would help.
  - IndexCharacterRight: 0
    IndexCharacterLeft: 0
    IndexCharacterFocus: 0
    IndexExpression: 0
    IndexEmotion: 0
    Text: Maybe she can tell the rest of the village to give her a handsome reward
      for dealing with the bandits!
  - IndexCharacterRight: 0
    IndexCharacterLeft: 0
    IndexCharacterFocus: 0
    IndexExpression: 0
    IndexEmotion: 0
    Text: Time to kill that fucker.
